      <title>Starmer对父母在法庭上提出质疑的私立学校税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/starmer-s-tax-on-private-schools-challenged-in-court-by-parents</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国总理凯尔·斯塔默（Keir Starmer）征服私立学校的税收被描述为前所未有的镇压，违反了该国的人权义务，这是对该计划的第一个实质性法院挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/starmer-s-tax-on-private-schools-challenged-in-court-by-parents</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 13:02:22 GMT</pubDate>
